# Optimal pH Predictor

This application predicts (badly) the optimal growth pH for proteins given their sequences

Input format:
```
sequence



MIKPSIFLMILILIGFVVGIITYNQSPLLFSLLIQVNYFVLRGDYLSLITSILVTNSFTDFIFNFISIWVIYYLFGSKAGKFEIVVFFISGILGNLLTLALFPPFTASAGASGGIFGVLSFYIIDDMLQFSRLDWNGLGLLIIVFVLSDIIPGVNYVAHIGGILGGILLALGRKRFLTTHYQK
```

Output format:
```
predictions
6.32
1.56
7.5
9.5
```
